    • ColorSensor

      public ColorSensor​(edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.I2C.Port port, double confidence, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.util.Color[] colors)
      Parameters:
      port - This is the the port of the sensor, you can grab it with (I2C.Port.kOnboard)
      confidence - This is a double in the range of [0.0 to 1.0] which the color sensor will use to make its prediction with.
      colors - This is an array of colors which you will pass to the ColorSensor so the program can create the proper predition of which color it sees.
